{
  "texts": [
    "14 For two years, Eugenia Kuyda -the founder of Replika-had been building Luka, a bot-based messaging app, initially designed for restaurant reservations.",
    "After a close friend died, friends discussed ways to honor his memory-ideas ranged from a coffee-table book of his life to a memorial website.",
    "Yet, to Kuyda, all these felt insufficient.",
    "Grieving, she reread the thousands of texts Mazurenko had sent her, finding comfort in them.",
    "She first did a chatbot emulating her deceased friend."
  ]
}